859
00:30:41,110 --> 00:30:41,670
Does it matter if I'm standing or not?

860
00:30:41,670 --> 00:30:42,830
I don't need you to serve me.

861
00:30:42,830 --> 00:30:44,470
Are you serving me tea?

862
00:30:44,470 --> 00:30:45,470
-I…
-I think you're sending me away.

863
00:30:45,470 --> 00:30:46,270
send me away?

864
00:30:50,070 --> 00:30:51,070
Yaya.

865
00:30:51,310 --> 00:30:51,950
Coming.

866
00:30:52,070 --> 00:30:52,790
Grandma,

867
00:30:52,790 --> 00:30:53,920
is this bowl okay?

868
00:30:53,920 --> 00:30:54,870
Sure. Rice on the roof is a good omen

869
00:30:54,870 --> 00:30:56,440
for wealth and prosperity.

870
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:57,700
Quick, put it up there.

871
00:30:57,750 --> 00:30:58,830
Make sure

872
00:30:58,830 --> 00:31:00,160
it's in the right place.

873
00:31:00,790 --> 00:31:01,920
Come on. Be careful.

874
00:31:04,310 --> 00:31:05,590
More to the left.

875
00:31:05,590 --> 00:31:06,240
Left, right?

876
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:07,270
-A little to the left.
-Mom.

877
00:31:07,270 --> 00:31:08,030
A little bit more.

878
00:31:08,030 --> 00:31:08,990
What era is this?

879
00:31:08,990 --> 00:31:10,590
You're still into superstitions.

880
00:31:10,590 --> 00:31:12,070
Ignoring feng shui is not okay.

881
00:31:12,070 --> 00:31:12,870
Mom, look at the mirror.

882
00:31:12,870 --> 00:31:13,590
Is this mirror okay?

883
00:31:13,590 --> 00:31:14,950
It has peonies on it.

884
00:31:15,030 --> 00:31:15,790
Great.

885
00:31:15,790 --> 00:31:17,910
Peonies symbolize wealth and prosperity.

886
00:31:17,910 --> 00:31:18,830
This mirror should be hung

887
00:31:18,830 --> 00:31:20,190
at the entrance.

888
00:31:20,190 --> 00:31:21,350
-Okay.
-It can ward off evil spirits.

889
00:31:21,350 --> 00:31:22,210
I'll hang it up.

890
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:24,870
Yaya, give me that stool.

891
00:31:24,870 --> 00:31:25,280
Here.

892
00:31:25,300 --> 00:31:26,340
Be careful.

893
00:31:27,860 --> 00:31:28,590
-Cheng Pengfei.
-Let me see.

894
00:31:28,590 --> 00:31:29,350
Let me see.

895
00:31:29,350 --> 00:31:29,950
-Good.
-Look.

896
00:31:29,950 --> 00:31:30,870
-Is it in the right place?
-You…

897
00:31:30,870 --> 00:31:31,350
What are you doing?

898
00:31:31,350 --> 00:31:32,190
You're

899
00:31:32,190 --> 00:31:32,950
a well-educated person.

900
00:31:32,950 --> 00:31:33,670
Why are you following along

901
00:31:33,670 --> 00:31:35,150
with this nonsense?

902
00:31:35,150 --> 00:31:36,290
I'm following the orders

903
00:31:36,290 --> 00:31:37,830
from your mother.

904
00:31:38,190 --> 00:31:39,590
What does

905
00:31:39,590 --> 00:31:41,090
filial piety mean?

906
00:31:41,280 --> 00:31:43,280
It means you have to go along with it.

907
00:31:43,850 --> 00:31:45,220
If you don't like it,

908
00:31:45,590 --> 00:31:46,470
we can take it down

909
00:31:46,470 --> 00:31:47,470
after she leaves.

910
00:31:48,100 --> 00:31:49,470
Come, come, come. Help me out.

911
00:31:49,470 --> 00:31:50,670
Come on.

912
00:31:51,290 --> 00:31:52,420
Open the door for me.

913
00:31:57,550 --> 00:31:58,750
I'm hanging it outside.

914
00:31:58,750 --> 00:32:01,080
I've seen other people have it hung up too.

915
00:32:02,620 --> 00:32:03,330
Slow down.

916
00:32:05,590 --> 00:32:07,030
What are you two doing?

917
00:32:07,030 --> 00:32:08,190
Where have you been?

918
00:32:08,590 --> 00:32:10,790
I was taking care of important matters.

919
00:32:11,030 --> 00:32:12,590
What important matters do you have?

920
00:32:12,590 --> 00:32:13,270
Where did you go?

921
00:32:13,270 --> 00:32:14,350
You were out all night.

922
00:32:14,350 --> 00:32:15,470
Mom, stop asking.

923
00:32:15,470 --> 00:32:16,370
You go ahead with what you're doing.

924
00:32:16,370 --> 00:32:17,770
If I don't care, who will?

925
00:32:18,210 --> 00:32:19,000
What were you doing?

926
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:19,550
Oh,

927
00:32:19,550 --> 00:32:21,610
and wash the duvet cover. It's dirty.

928
00:32:22,790 --> 00:32:24,360
Tell me, what were you doing?

929
00:32:24,360 --> 00:32:25,590
Mom, I didn't do anything.

930
00:32:25,590 --> 00:32:26,430
Stop bothering me.

931
00:32:26,430 --> 00:32:27,430
No, you have to tell me

932
00:32:27,430 --> 00:32:28,510
what you were doing.

933
00:32:28,510 --> 00:32:29,230
Hello?

934
00:32:29,630 --> 00:32:30,300
Dad.

935
00:32:31,460 --> 00:32:32,370
Which train?

936
00:32:32,770 --> 00:32:34,170
Alright, alright, alright.

937
00:32:34,170 --> 00:32:35,430
You want to talk to Mom?

938
00:32:35,870 --> 00:32:37,430
Mom, Mom.

939
00:32:38,070 --> 00:32:39,150
Dad's on the phone.

940
00:32:39,750 --> 00:32:40,310
You...

941
00:32:40,310 --> 00:32:41,410
I've already arranged it.

942
00:32:41,410 --> 00:32:42,710
He'll be coming over by train soon.

943
00:32:42,710 --> 00:32:43,910
Don't stop him again.

944
00:32:44,640 --> 00:32:45,700
Why are you coming?

945
00:32:46,590 --> 00:32:48,270
Why do you follow me everywhere?

946
00:32:48,270 --> 00:32:49,090
-Well…
-Can you give me

947
00:32:49,090 --> 00:32:50,540
some personal space?

948
00:32:51,270 --> 00:32:52,400
Did you smoke again?

949
00:32:53,430 --> 00:32:54,670
I can smell it.

950
00:32:55,310 --> 00:32:56,370
Where's the thing?

951
00:32:57,190 --> 00:32:57,880
This box.

952
00:32:57,880 --> 00:32:58,920
Let Wang know about it.

953
00:32:58,920 --> 00:33:00,030
See if there are any cars going

954
00:33:00,030 --> 00:33:01,510
towards your place in the next few days.

955
00:33:01,510 --> 00:33:02,390
Have them deliver it.

956
00:33:02,390 --> 00:33:03,150
What's this?

957
00:33:03,150 --> 00:33:05,590
New Year's goods.

958
00:33:06,600 --> 00:33:07,350
I also got

959
00:33:07,350 --> 00:33:08,590
two extra packs of red dates for Mom

960
00:33:08,590 --> 00:33:10,070
to boost her health.

961
00:33:10,950 --> 00:33:11,910
And these—

962
00:33:13,450 --> 00:33:14,540
for which leader

963
00:33:15,130 --> 00:33:16,230
likes what kind of liquor,

964
00:33:16,230 --> 00:33:17,910
cigarettes, or tea,

965
00:33:17,930 --> 00:33:19,650
I've noted everything clearly.

966
00:33:19,650 --> 00:33:21,150
Even the names

967
00:33:21,150 --> 00:33:22,310
are written down.

968
00:33:22,790 --> 00:33:23,950
Nowadays, it's not just about

969
00:33:23,950 --> 00:33:24,990
celebrating the New Year;

970
00:33:24,990 --> 00:33:27,250
it's about maintaining relationships.

971
00:33:28,020 --> 00:33:29,020
Gifts are not

972
00:33:29,050 --> 00:33:29,870
so easily accepted now.

973
00:33:29,870 --> 00:33:31,510
We're just giving some New Year goods

974
00:33:31,510 --> 00:33:33,030
to show our sincerity.

975
00:33:34,590 --> 00:33:35,350
I always feel like that little notebook

976
00:33:35,350 --> 00:33:36,300
is like evidence.

977
00:33:36,300 --> 00:33:36,840
What?

978
00:33:38,490 --> 00:33:39,580
Alright, alright, marrying you wasn't a mistake.

979
00:33:39,580 --> 00:33:40,310
I'm leaving.

980
00:33:41,940 --> 00:33:42,870
Bye.

981
00:33:43,620 --> 00:33:44,420
Wait a minute.

982
00:33:45,230 --> 00:33:46,630
Don't tell Mom

983
00:33:46,630 --> 00:33:47,840
it's because I didn't want to go back.

984
00:33:47,840 --> 00:33:49,900
Just say it's because you're on duty.

985
00:33:50,660 --> 00:33:51,720
Got it?

986
00:33:52,380 --> 00:33:53,320
This lie

987
00:33:53,760 --> 00:33:54,690
is very precise.

988
00:33:54,880 --> 00:33:55,450
Okay.

989
00:34:04,790 --> 00:34:05,300
Here.

990
00:34:05,990 --> 00:34:06,720
Give it to me.

991
00:34:07,250 --> 00:34:09,000
Mom, my brother is back.

992
00:34:09,020 --> 00:34:09,900
Aunt Yue.

993
00:34:11,199 --> 00:34:12,370
Tao, you're back.

994
00:34:12,550 --> 00:34:12,989
Come in quickly.

995
00:34:12,989 --> 00:34:14,360
Come in quickly.

996
00:34:15,909 --> 00:34:17,050
Didn't run into your dad?

997
00:34:17,050 --> 00:34:18,590
He said he went to buy alcohol.

998
00:34:18,590 --> 00:34:19,750
-No.
-He wants to drink with you tonight.

999
00:34:19,750 --> 00:34:21,310
Dad still loves to drink.

1000
00:34:21,630 --> 00:34:23,570
Come on, come on. You should drink tonight.

1001
00:34:23,570 --> 00:34:24,280
Your dad has been

1002
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:25,600
looking forward to your return.

1003
00:34:25,600 --> 00:34:26,440
Take off your coat.

1004
00:34:26,440 --> 00:34:27,679
It's warm at home.

1005
00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:28,870
How's your health and Dad's?

1006
00:34:28,870 --> 00:34:30,110
We're doing fine.

1007
00:34:30,210 --> 00:34:31,530
Have you grown taller,

1008
00:34:31,560 --> 00:34:32,120
Tao?

1009
00:34:32,139 --> 00:34:32,980
Have I?

1010
00:34:33,989 --> 00:34:35,429
So tall, isn't it?

1011
00:34:36,639 --> 00:34:37,630
Tonight we'll have dumplings

1012
00:34:37,630 --> 00:34:39,110
with your favorite lamb filling.

1013
00:34:39,110 --> 00:34:40,239
Thank you, Aunt Yue.

1014
00:34:40,510 --> 00:34:41,429
Go wash your hands and face

1015
00:34:41,429 --> 00:34:42,590
in the bathroom.

1016
00:34:42,719 --> 00:34:43,830
The dumplings will be ready soon.

1017
00:34:43,830 --> 00:34:44,400
Okay.

1018
00:34:44,460 --> 00:34:45,889
Aunt Yue, let me help you

1019
00:34:46,429 --> 00:34:47,400
-Let me help you.
-No need.

1020
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,880
Go talk to your sister for a while.

1021
00:34:48,880 --> 00:34:49,679
Rest for a bit.

1022
00:34:49,679 --> 00:34:50,320
No, no.

1023
00:34:50,320 --> 00:34:51,159
No need, no need.

1024
00:34:51,159 --> 00:34:51,760
Let me see

1025
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:53,620
what nice things you've brought.

1026
00:34:54,909 --> 00:34:56,699
I bought a nice gift for you.

1027
00:34:56,840 --> 00:34:57,430
What is it?

1028
00:34:57,430 --> 00:34:58,290
Open it and see.

1029
00:35:00,250 --> 00:35:01,290
So delicate.

1030
00:35:03,480 --> 00:35:04,280
Do you like it?

1031
00:35:05,150 --> 00:35:06,490
Yes.

1032
00:35:15,940 --> 00:35:17,420
It hurts.

1033
00:35:17,670 --> 00:35:18,790
Open the door.

1034
00:35:17,740 --> 00:35:19,660
[Linchuan Tonghua]

1035
00:35:22,800 --> 00:35:24,730
Do you still want to play with this?

1036
00:35:25,900 --> 00:35:26,460
Look.

1037
00:35:26,530 --> 00:35:28,000
There's a longer one at Sister's place,

1038
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:29,140
even longer than this one.

1039
00:35:29,140 --> 00:35:30,140
Come on, pull it.

1040
00:35:31,950 --> 00:35:33,150
Make it shorter.

1041
00:35:34,460 --> 00:35:35,270
It's not fun?

1042
00:35:35,430 --> 00:35:36,870
Here, put this on.

1043
00:35:37,650 --> 00:35:38,230
Yes.

1044
00:35:43,030 --> 00:35:43,740
Listen.

1045
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:45,620
You don't need to bring anything.

1046
00:35:46,720 --> 00:35:47,290
Grandma's here.

1047
00:35:47,290 --> 00:35:48,750
How can I go empty-handed?

1048
00:35:48,970 --> 00:35:49,910
I'll steam some buns

1049
00:35:49,910 --> 00:35:51,570
and everyone can have a taste.

1050
00:35:57,570 --> 00:35:59,300
I'll make a little bear for you.

1051
00:36:03,940 --> 00:36:04,670
Brother!

1052
00:36:06,350 --> 00:36:08,510
Grandpa, Grandpa, my brother is back.

1053
00:36:12,290 --> 00:36:13,010
Brother!

1054
00:36:17,880 --> 00:36:19,080
Who cut your hair?

1055
00:36:20,460 --> 00:36:21,550
My classmates.

1056
00:36:22,770 --> 00:36:24,700
They're much better at it than I am.

1057
00:36:26,880 --> 00:36:27,580
Dawa.

1058
00:36:27,610 --> 00:36:28,250
Grandpa.

1059
00:36:37,390 --> 00:36:38,920
It's good that you're back.

1060
00:36:39,060 --> 00:36:40,490
You must have suffered

1061
00:36:41,610 --> 00:36:42,810
these past two years.

1062
00:36:44,270 --> 00:36:46,020
Not at all. What suffering?

1063
00:36:47,700 --> 00:36:49,100
Let me tell you, Grandpa,

1064
00:36:49,170 --> 00:36:50,970
the house I built is really nice.

1065
00:36:51,020 --> 00:36:52,160
It's ten stories high

1066
00:36:52,160 --> 00:36:53,290
and has an elevator.

1067
00:36:53,530 --> 00:36:54,790
Just press the button,

1068
00:36:54,790 --> 00:36:56,320
and whoosh, you're on the tenth floor.

1069
00:36:56,320 --> 00:36:57,290
Really?

1070
00:36:57,310 --> 00:36:58,070
Of course.

1071
00:36:58,410 --> 00:36:59,350
The wind is strong outside.

1072
00:36:59,350 --> 00:37:00,530
Come on, let's go inside.

1073
00:37:00,530 --> 00:37:02,200
-Let’s talk inside.
-Let’s go inside.

1074
00:37:02,200 --> 00:37:03,880
Grandpa, how's your leg?

1075
00:37:04,030 --> 00:37:05,140
It's good, good.

1076
00:37:05,420 --> 00:37:06,530
As soon as you're back,

1077
00:37:06,530 --> 00:37:07,810
everything is better.

1078
00:37:08,960 --> 00:37:09,770
Where is Babao?

1079
00:37:09,770 --> 00:37:10,890
He went on a blind date.

1080
00:37:10,890 --> 00:37:12,010
Blind date?

1081
00:37:12,040 --> 00:37:14,050
The Wei family has a little black dog,

1082
00:37:14,050 --> 00:37:15,490
and Babao, who's so useless,

1083
00:37:15,490 --> 00:37:17,220
keeps going over to visit them.

1084
00:37:17,380 --> 00:37:19,000
Tonight we'll have dumplings.

1085
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:19,530
Okay!

1086
00:37:21,070 --> 00:37:22,620
You bought the wrong ticket.

1087
00:37:22,620 --> 00:37:23,560
Wrong?

1088
00:37:24,260 --> 00:37:25,350
Isn't it Tonghua?

1089
00:37:26,010 --> 00:37:26,860
Tongliao.

1090
00:37:27,820 --> 00:37:29,380
It's my fault. I remembered it wrong.

1091
00:37:29,380 --> 00:37:30,850
I lined up all night and didn't get it.

1092
00:37:30,850 --> 00:37:31,680
I'll buy another one.

1093
00:37:31,680 --> 00:37:32,350
Come back.

1094
00:37:32,610 --> 00:37:33,570
No need to buy another.

1095
00:37:33,570 --> 00:37:35,260
You won't be able to buy it now anyway.

1096
00:37:35,260 --> 00:37:36,590
It's fine if it's wrong.

1097
00:37:36,930 --> 00:37:38,910
So what? You're going to Tonghua?

1098
00:37:39,010 --> 00:37:40,600
Why would I go to Tonghua?

1099
00:37:40,700 --> 00:37:41,930
I'll stay here.

1100
00:37:41,970 --> 00:37:43,880
I can celebrate New Year here as well.

1101
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:44,840
How much did you spend?

1102
00:37:44,840 --> 00:37:45,440
I'll give it to you.

1103
00:37:45,440 --> 00:37:47,570
No, no, you don't need to give me money.

1104
00:37:47,950 --> 00:37:49,010
First, I bought the wrong one.

1105
00:37:49,010 --> 00:37:49,600
Even if I got the right one,

1106
00:37:49,600 --> 00:37:50,830
I can't accept your money.

1107
00:37:50,830 --> 00:37:51,990
Don't say that.

1108
00:37:52,010 --> 00:37:53,530
I can't take advantage of you for nothing.

1109
00:37:53,530 --> 00:37:54,780
What advantage?

1110
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:56,110
We're friends.

1111
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:58,340
The main thing is that you,

1112
00:37:58,490 --> 00:37:59,280
the pillar of the school,

1113
00:37:59,280 --> 00:37:59,740
our diligent gardener,

1114
00:37:59,740 --> 00:38:00,570
shouldn't spend New Year alone.

1115
00:38:00,570 --> 00:38:01,770
It would be terrible.

1116
00:38:05,780 --> 00:38:06,890
Why don't you come to my place?

1117
00:38:06,890 --> 00:38:08,070
My family is large, and it's very lively.

1118
00:38:08,070 --> 00:38:08,950
We can celebrate together.

1119
00:38:08,950 --> 00:38:10,130
That's inappropriate.

1120
00:38:10,130 --> 00:38:11,100
What's inappropriate about it?

1121
00:38:11,100 --> 00:38:11,620
The kids

1122
00:38:11,640 --> 00:38:12,540
are familiar with you.

1123
00:38:12,540 --> 00:38:13,700
It's just that...

1124
00:38:13,730 --> 00:38:15,240
I haven't finished tidying up.

1125
00:38:15,240 --> 00:38:17,210
I haven't even put up the Spring Festival couplets yet.

1126
00:38:17,210 --> 00:38:17,880
That's it?

1127
00:38:18,580 --> 00:38:19,910
Let me take care of that.

1128
00:38:20,410 --> 00:38:21,640
Not a big deal.

1129
00:38:23,560 --> 00:38:24,600
Fried chicken.

1130
00:38:24,900 --> 00:38:26,050
I just learned it this year.

1131
00:38:26,050 --> 00:38:27,980
It's great. It smells really good.

1132
00:38:29,750 --> 00:38:30,590
Daiyu.

1133
00:38:31,110 --> 00:38:31,990
Daiyu.

1134
00:38:32,720 --> 00:38:33,660
I'm coming.

1135
00:38:33,680 --> 00:38:34,320
Dad.

1136
00:38:34,600 --> 00:38:35,260
Dad, you're here.

1137
00:38:35,260 --> 00:38:36,390
Come on in.

1138
00:38:37,440 --> 00:38:37,950
Here.

1139
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:39,420
Take these slippers.

1140
00:38:39,420 --> 00:38:40,620
Give them to me.

1141
00:38:40,650 --> 00:38:41,920
-Take it.
-Was the trip smooth?

1142
00:38:41,920 --> 00:38:42,950
Yes.

1143
00:38:43,110 --> 00:38:44,020
Good.

1144
00:38:44,660 --> 00:38:45,400
Mom.

1145
00:38:47,950 --> 00:38:49,190
Take off your coat.

1146
00:38:52,280 --> 00:38:53,290
Where did she go?

1147
00:39:06,630 --> 00:39:07,830
I'm still cooking.

1148
00:39:31,120 --> 00:39:32,850
Pengfei, where's that old man?

1149
00:39:35,550 --> 00:39:36,920
The bag is here.

1150
00:39:38,600 --> 00:39:39,520
Oh my god.

1151
00:39:40,320 --> 00:39:41,470
Are you looking for me?

1152
00:39:41,470 --> 00:39:42,630
Who is looking for you?

1153
00:39:42,630 --> 00:39:44,350
Move aside. I'm working.

1154
00:39:46,450 --> 00:39:47,780
What are you doing here?

1155
00:39:48,040 --> 00:39:49,250
What am I doing here?

1156
00:39:49,630 --> 00:39:52,030
I came to spend New Year's with my daughter.

1157
00:39:52,080 --> 00:39:53,100
What else would I be doing?

1158
00:39:53,100 --> 00:39:54,380
That's my daughter.

1159
00:39:55,290 --> 00:39:56,850
Her name is Jia Daiyu.

1160
00:39:56,950 --> 00:39:58,700
My name is Jia Xikui.

1161
00:39:58,730 --> 00:40:00,040
We both have the surname Jia.

1162
00:40:00,040 --> 00:40:01,200
She's my daughter,

1163
00:40:01,300 --> 00:40:02,220
born to me.

1164
00:40:02,250 --> 00:40:03,790
If I were to marry someone with the surname Wang,

1165
00:40:03,790 --> 00:40:05,470
she'd be Wang Daiyu.

1166
00:40:07,040 --> 00:40:08,100
Which Wang would dare

1167
00:40:08,100 --> 00:40:09,660
marry an old lady like you?

1168
00:40:10,530 --> 00:40:11,600
Well then, why don't you divorce me

1169
00:40:11,600 --> 00:40:12,720
and see if anyone will marry me?

1170
00:40:12,720 --> 00:40:13,320
You...

1171
00:40:13,660 --> 00:40:16,480
You're bringing up divorce at my daughter's place?

1172
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:17,720
It's New Year's Eve.

1173
00:40:17,740 --> 00:40:18,690
Why are you talking about divorce?

1174
00:40:18,690 --> 00:40:19,490
That's right.

1175
00:40:19,530 --> 00:40:20,500
It's inauspicious.

1176
00:40:20,500 --> 00:40:21,830
Let's not talk about it.

1177
00:40:22,240 --> 00:40:23,400
Come on, Dad, take off your coat.

1178
00:40:23,400 --> 00:40:24,330
Your mom is always involved

1179
00:40:24,330 --> 00:40:25,740
in inauspicious things.

1180
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:27,730
He's just an unlucky person.

1181
00:40:27,900 --> 00:40:29,060
He's always arguing with me,

1182
00:40:29,060 --> 00:40:30,410
all day long.

1183
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:31,390
Mom, enough.

1184
00:40:31,420 --> 00:40:32,020
Sit there.

1185
00:40:32,050 --> 00:40:33,420
It's always you

1186
00:40:33,440 --> 00:40:34,510
who starts the arguments.

1187
00:40:34,510 --> 00:40:35,830
-Dad.
-It's you.

1188
00:40:35,860 --> 00:40:36,910
Dad, don't be angry.

1189
00:40:36,910 --> 00:40:38,750
It's New Year.

1190
00:40:39,370 --> 00:40:39,970
Come.

1191
00:40:40,350 --> 00:40:43,010
-Dad, have a seat.
-Sit down and drink some water.

1192
00:40:43,010 --> 00:40:44,180
Water?

1193
00:40:44,920 --> 00:40:45,500
What do you mean?

1194
00:40:45,500 --> 00:40:46,900
You want me to drink this?

1195
00:40:47,440 --> 00:40:48,640
Alright, Dad.

1196
00:40:48,670 --> 00:40:50,390
Dad, let me make you some coffee.

1197
00:40:50,390 --> 00:40:52,990
No. I want water and tea.

1198
00:40:53,410 --> 00:40:54,670
Give me a cup of coffee.

1199
00:40:55,230 --> 00:40:55,790
Okay.

1200
00:40:55,810 --> 00:40:56,530
Old woman,

1201
00:40:56,560 --> 00:40:58,600
when did you develop this habit?

1202
00:40:58,680 --> 00:41:00,460
You can't sleep after drinking it.

1203
00:41:00,460 --> 00:41:01,500
It's good then.

1204
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:02,310
I'll play with you.

1205
00:41:02,310 --> 00:41:03,390
Play with me?

1206
00:41:03,410 --> 00:41:04,470
You'll torture me.

1207
00:41:07,770 --> 00:41:08,440
Is it good?

1208
00:41:09,710 --> 00:41:10,400
Yes.

1209
00:41:11,640 --> 00:41:12,140
Okay.

1210
00:41:17,700 --> 00:41:18,270
Here.

1211
00:41:19,150 --> 00:41:20,080
Give me the glue.

1212
00:41:23,010 --> 00:41:24,570
You don't stick it here.

1213
00:41:24,670 --> 00:41:25,930
You don't understand.

1214
00:41:25,950 --> 00:41:28,190
This is called “seeing fortune when you look up.”

1215
00:41:28,190 --> 00:41:29,350
Be careful.

1216
00:41:29,370 --> 00:41:30,290
No need.

1217
00:41:30,370 --> 00:41:31,830
I can even jump to stick it on.

1218
00:41:31,830 --> 00:41:32,740
Come on.

1219
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:34,720
You're not even tall enough on the chair.

1220
00:41:34,720 --> 00:41:35,340
How about this?

1221
00:41:35,340 --> 00:41:36,340
Go take out the trash.

1222
00:41:36,340 --> 00:41:38,160
Don't leave any trash until next year.

1223
00:41:38,160 --> 00:41:39,880
Really? That's a thing too?

1224
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:44,440
Be careful.

1225
00:41:44,460 --> 00:41:45,190
Don't worry.

1226
00:41:57,510 --> 00:41:58,430
Baoshan.

1227
00:41:59,080 --> 00:42:00,210
Get up!

1228
00:42:00,580 --> 00:42:01,440
Don't touch me.

1229
00:42:01,750 --> 00:42:02,810
Where are you hurt?

1230
00:42:04,090 --> 00:42:04,840
Nowhere.

1231
00:42:05,150 --> 00:42:06,610
Just tired, taking a rest.

1232
00:42:11,680 --> 00:42:13,320
It's New Year's Eve again.

1233
00:42:13,530 --> 00:42:14,530
Linqi Oilfield

1234
00:42:14,560 --> 00:42:16,190
wishes all oil workers

1235
00:42:16,320 --> 00:42:17,560
a joyful family reunion

1236
00:42:17,560 --> 00:42:19,020
and happiness and health.

1237
00:42:19,050 --> 00:42:21,280
We're sending New Year's greetings in advance.

1238
00:42:21,280 --> 00:42:23,720
Happy New Year to everyone.

1239
00:42:28,540 --> 00:42:29,410
Not everyone is happy

1240
00:42:29,410 --> 00:42:31,320
as the New Year approaches.

1241
00:42:31,720 --> 00:42:33,310
Some carry worries

1242
00:42:33,930 --> 00:42:35,170
from the past year

1243
00:42:35,190 --> 00:42:36,400
into the new one.

1244
00:42:36,890 --> 00:42:38,580
We Chinese often say,

1245
00:42:38,870 --> 00:42:41,000
that on New Year's, we should be happy.

1246
00:42:41,110 --> 00:42:42,440
All the misfortunes

1247
00:42:42,690 --> 00:42:43,490
of the past year

1248
00:42:43,490 --> 00:42:44,690
seem to dissipate

1249
00:42:44,720 --> 00:42:45,720
with the New Year.

1250
00:42:46,120 --> 00:42:48,050
That's the meaning of the New Year.

1251
00:42:48,250 --> 00:42:49,840
I always love the New Year.

1252
00:42:50,140 --> 00:42:51,460
I never let unhappy things

1253
00:42:51,460 --> 00:42:52,690
carry over into the new year.

1254
00:42:52,690 --> 00:42:53,480
No matter how bad

1255
00:42:53,480 --> 00:42:54,650
the past year was,

1256
00:42:54,890 --> 00:42:56,220
It's all in the past now.

1257
00:42:56,540 --> 00:42:57,730
We must believe that

1258
00:42:58,250 --> 00:42:59,850
the coming year brings hope.

1259
00:43:00,060 --> 00:43:02,130
Happy New Year. Lucky every year.
